episodes.title: King Charles HAD to be ruthless in stripping Andrew of his title - scandal was a ticking time bomb
episodes.description:
Royal expert Dickie Arbiter weighs in on the monumental decision by King Charles to strip Prince Andrew of his remaining titles and honours, forcing him out of Royal Lodge.

Arbiter calls the scandal a 'ticking time bomb' that the late Queen Elizabeth II left for Charles, forcing him to take a drastic, ruthless step to protect the Crown's reputation.

This video contains: 
00:00 - How Princess Eugenie and Princess Beatrice will be coping.
00:27 - The statement from Buckingham Palace. 
00:55 - Charles was left with 'ticking time bomb' from The Queen.
02:00 - The royal family will 'survive this'.
03:43 - What can we expect to happen next?

episodes.title: I was trapped in a cruel cult and forced to give ALL my money to the leaders
episodes.description:
A CULT victim has described how brain-washed members donated all their money and were subjected to bizarre ‘teaching’ videos of the sect's leaders in hot tubs.

Richard Turner was ironically working for a modern slavery support charity tied to the ominous Hope City Church when he was inadvertently drawn into its dark web.
